---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
import Container from "@/components/container.astro";
---

<Layout title="Privacy Policy" description="Privacy Policy for PgDesigner — how we handle your data on pgdesigner.io.">
  <Container>
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto pt-16 pb-24 prose-custom">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-heading">Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-muted">Last updated: April 3, 2026</p>

      <div class="mt-10 space-y-8 text-body text-sm leading-relaxed">
        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-heading mb-3">1. Overview</h2>
          <p>
            This Privacy Policy describes how MyShows Inc. ("we", "us", "our") collects, uses, and protects information
            when you visit <a href="https://pgdesigner.io" class="text-accent-text hover:underline">pgdesigner.io</a>
            ("Website") or use PgDesigner ("Software").
            "vmkteam" and "PgDesigner" are trade names of MyShows Inc., a Delaware corporation.
          </p>
          <p class="mt-2">
            We are committed to protecting your privacy. We collect only the minimum data necessary to operate the Website
            and process purchases.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-heading mb-3">2. Desktop Application</h2>
          <p>
            PgDesigner is an <strong>offline-first desktop application</strong>. The Software:
          </p>
          <ul class="mt-2 ml-4 list-disc space-y-1">
            <li>Does not require an account or login</li>
            <li>Does not collect or transmit any personal data</li>
            <li>Does not include telemetry, analytics, or crash reporting</li>
            <li>Does not phone home or check for updates automatically</li>
            <li>Stores all your data (schema files, settings) locally on your machine</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-2">
            We have no access to your schemas, database credentials, or any other data you work with in PgDesigner.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-heading mb-3">3. Website Analytics</h2>
          <p>
            We use <strong>Google Analytics 4</strong> (measurement ID: G-HFQ9KWZNVN) on our Website to understand
            how visitors find and use pgdesigner.io. Google Analytics may collect:
          </p>
          <ul class="mt-2 ml-4 list-disc space-y-1">
            <li>Pages visited and time spent</li>
            <li>Referring website or search terms</li>
            <li>Approximate geographic location (country/city level)</li>
            <li>Device type, browser, and operating system</li>
            <li>An anonymous client identifier</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-2">
            This data is used solely to improve our Website and understand our audience. We do not use it to personally identify visitors.
            For more information, see
            <a href="https://policies.google.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-accent-text hover:underline">Google's Privacy Policy</a>.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-heading mb-3">4. Purchases</h2>
          <p>
            License purchases are processed by
            <a href="https://stripe.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-accent-text hover:underline">Stripe</a>.
            When you make a purchase, Stripe collects and processes:
          </p>
          <ul class="mt-2 ml-4 list-disc space-y-1">
            <li>Name and email address</li>
            <li>Billing address</li>
            <li>Payment information (credit card, etc.)</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-2">
            We receive your name, email, and order details for license fulfillment and support purposes.
            We do not store or have access to your full payment card details.
            For more information, see
            <a href="https://stripe.com/privacy" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="text-accent-text hover:underline">Stripe's Privacy Policy</a>.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-heading mb-3">5. Cookies</h2>
          <p>
            Our Website uses the following cookies:
          </p>
          <ul class="mt-2 ml-4 list-disc space-y-1">
            <li><strong>Google Analytics cookies</strong> (<code class="text-xs">_ga</code>, <code class="text-xs">_ga_*</code>) — used for website analytics as described in Section 3</li>
            <li><strong>Theme preference</strong> — stored in localStorage (not a cookie), used to remember your dark/light mode choice</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-2">
            We do not use advertising cookies or third-party tracking cookies.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-heading mb-3">6. Email Communication</h2>
          <p>
            If you purchase a license, we may send you:
          </p>
          <ul class="mt-2 ml-4 list-disc space-y-1">
            <li>Purchase confirmation and receipt</li>
            <li>Important product updates (e.g., major releases, security patches)</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-2">
            We do not send marketing newsletters. If you contact us at
            <a href="mailto:support@pgdesigner.io" class="text-accent-text hover:underline">support@pgdesigner.io</a>,
            we store your email only for the purpose of responding to your inquiry.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-heading mb-3">7. Data Sharing</h2>
          <p>
            We do not sell, rent, or share your personal information with third parties, except:
          </p>
          <ul class="mt-2 ml-4 list-disc space-y-1">
            <li><strong>Stripe</strong> — for payment processing</li>
            <li><strong>Google Analytics</strong> — for anonymized website usage data</li>
            <li><strong>Legal requirements</strong> — if required by law or to protect our rights</li>
          </ul>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-heading mb-3">8. Data Retention</h2>
          <p>
            Purchase records (name, email, order details) are retained for the duration of your license and as required
            for accounting and legal purposes. Website analytics data is retained according to Google Analytics default settings (14 months).
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-heading mb-3">9. Your Rights</h2>
          <p>
            Depending on your jurisdiction, you may have the right to:
          </p>
          <ul class="mt-2 ml-4 list-disc space-y-1">
            <li>Access the personal data we hold about you</li>
            <li>Request correction or deletion of your data</li>
            <li>Object to or restrict processing of your data</li>
            <li>Request a copy of your data in a portable format</li>
          </ul>
          <p class="mt-2">
            To exercise any of these rights, contact us at
            <a href="mailto:support@pgdesigner.io" class="text-accent-text hover:underline">support@pgdesigner.io</a>.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-heading mb-3">10. Children's Privacy</h2>
          <p>
            Our Website and Software are not directed at children under the age of 16.
            We do not knowingly collect personal information from children.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-heading mb-3">11. Changes to This Policy</h2>
          <p>
            We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. The updated version will be posted on this page with a revised
            "Last updated" date.
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-heading mb-3">12. Data Controller</h2>
          <p>
            The data controller for information collected through the Website and purchase process is:
          </p>
          <p class="mt-2 text-xs text-muted">
            MyShows Inc.<br />
            2810 N Church St, PMB 92198<br />
            Wilmington, Delaware 19802-4447 USA<br />
            Email: <a href="mailto:support@pgdesigner.io" class="text-accent-text hover:underline">support@pgdesigner.io</a>
          </p>
        </section>

        <section>
          <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-heading mb-3">13. Contact</h2>
          <p>
            If you have questions about this Privacy Policy, contact us at
            <a href="mailto:support@pgdesigner.io" class="text-accent-text hover:underline">support@pgdesigner.io</a>.
          </p>
        </section>
      </div>
    </div>
  </Container>
</Layout>
